5fec43a5f906a285b125e7b3c","tid":18004,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T10:08:29.000Z","msg":"I don't want 三支香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9c2a01f27a597b9dedf42ab3b9bb1679b1d9221","tid":18004,"uid":22402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T10:14:01.000Z","msg":"Apple router太貴買唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088b1d0b3c37fe7281af79140b2e3504d6be21bc","tid":18004,"uid":44,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T10:41:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實。。。。。市面上仲有好多好野。。。<br />\n<br />\n各位大哥又俾得起AE or TC既價，大把有得選。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNetgear: R7000 or above<br />\nGoogle Wifi, OnHub....<br />\n<br />\nEtc</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSad but true<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a1696d6e25333b26ab387ba179b2ae82e09942a","tid":18004,"uid":44,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T10:46:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>airport extreme + time capsule , apple network 嘢好耐用，又冇 hang 過機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩樣一齊用定點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一齊用，extreme 用開擺廳， tc 放房做backup同當hubs share LAN 比幾部腦+ps4<br />\n<br />\n屋企得300尺但干擾好大，冇主力牆房個wifi 一樣收得差，唔extend 個wifi 或者用番LAN ，打機會delay , download 嘢都好慢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n300尺但干擾好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又hub 又extend 打機咩仲delay<br />\nSet 完咁樣幾多ping 呀"},{"pid":"acaf40cf8a2a2e8804c165e235e3ab24a306215c","tid":18004,"uid":37097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T11:46:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>airport extreme + time capsule , apple network 嘢好耐用，又冇 hang 過機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩樣一齊用定點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一齊用，extreme 用開擺廳， tc 放房做backup同當hubs share LAN 比幾部腦+ps4<br />\n<br />\n屋企得300尺但干擾好大，冇主力牆房個wifi 一樣收得差，唔extend 個wifi 或者用番LAN ，打機會delay , download 嘢都好慢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n300尺但干擾好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又hub 又extend 打機咩仲delay<br />\nSet 完咁樣幾多ping 呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nrouter 放廳電視櫃頂, 格左塊木板既房用wifi 仲慢過4g<br />\n之前用tplink, buffalo, linksys 2-3天線router, 係廳無遮擋情況下, 有d位都收唔爆, 轉左extreme gen 5先收得爆<br />\n<br />\n無為意幾多ping, 但ext 左個wifi, 係房用wifi download 野快番好多....<br />\nps4 插lan 定係wifi 都好, 打fifa 唔使因為network問題lag 先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以前計黎, apple router 值得科水過而家, 早5-6年 wifi 接收, lan2lan/wan2lan, airport 都比唔少定用router 做得好<br />\n而家賣點真係穩定性, 易setup 同埋time machine還原成功率比nas高, 其他方面亦都不過不失"},{"pid":"8bffa8f2ead3dd909a97277686d5a2e78848a17f","tid":18004,"uid":408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T11:52:56.000Z","msg":"用緊airport extreme但又想backup部macbook,<br />\n買唔買time capsule好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e9eae6f9240066c6dc290a2f9c0c754dbbf792","tid":18004,"uid":37097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:15:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用緊airport extreme但又想backup部macbook,<br />\n買唔買time capsule好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你唔怕煩, 可以插隻ext hdd 做time machine<br />\n用airport extreme  / time capsule / nas 係貪番到屋企, 認到個time machine server 就會自己搞, 唔使理佢"},{"pid":"dc3bfa57e450e99116b08ffcbabda4d9751d08fc","tid":18004,"uid":24785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:16:34.000Z","msg":"Google Wifi"},{"pid":"5eabd27c